---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken Strips with Roasted Veggie Rice & Corn Cobs
description: Take your tastebuds on a trip to Portugal with this colourful feast. An easy marinade on the chicken, veggies roasted to sweet perfection and smokey aioli is what it's all about.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dfb032bc840bc243c051f6b-697ac4cd.jpg
